; A. Description
;    A list of commands here configures ADC and generates burst capture interrupt.
;
; B. Preparation
;    Connecting target port with a suitable instrument.
;
; C. Prerequisite Example (abov_example_config.h)
;    1. ADC
;
; D. Default Port
;    1. ADC0    : PA0 (AN0)
;               : PA1 (AN1)
;               : PA2 (AN2)
;
; For more information, read a user's manual of the target device carefully.
;
; ADC0
; 1. Channel                    : 0
;
; 2. Clock                      : [ 0 p 64 ]
;    Source                     : p (Peripheral Clock)
;    Peripheral Clock Divide    : 64
;
; 3. Config                     : [ config 0 i b a 8 0 ]
;    Operation                  : i (Interrupt)
;    Mode                       : b (Burst)
;    Base Trigger Source        : a (ADC Instant Start)
;    Sequence Count             : 8
;    Sampling Time              : 0
;
; 4. Seq                        : [ 0 a 0 0 ]
;    Trigger Source             : a (ADC Instant Start)
;    Sequence Number            : 0
;    Input Channel              : 0
;
; ADC0
sendln 'cm adc'
mpause 30
sendln 'uninit 0'
mpause 30
sendln 'init 0'
mpause 30
sendln 'clk 0 p 64'
mpause 30
sendln 'config 0 i b a 8 0'
mpause 30
sendln 'seq 0 a 0 0'
mpause 30
sendln 'seq 0 a 1 1'
mpause 30
sendln 'seq 0 a 2 2'
mpause 30
sendln 'seq 0 a 3 3'
mpause 30
sendln 'seq 0 a 4 4'
mpause 30
sendln 'seq 0 a 5 5'
mpause 30
sendln 'seq 0 a 6 6'
mpause 30
sendln 'seq 0 a 7 7'
mpause 30
sendln 'start 0'
pause 2 
sendln 'dump 0'
